{"tid":756101,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"破球會紀錄！白禮頓 1.8億簽伊朗前鋒","createTime":"2018-07-25T17:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T07:09:06.000Z","uid":62073,"like":9,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"33ca0fe3e8d95b6684b74fa5989a507947a46239","tid":756101,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T17:58:21.000Z","msg":"白禮頓迎來一單重磅收購！這支英超球會周三宣佈，從荷甲球會阿爾克馬爾簽入伊朗前鋒查漢巴克殊，與他簽下5年合約，轉會費據報為1,700萬鎊（約1.8億港元），為球會有史以來最貴的收購。<br />\n<br />\n查漢巴克殊為上屆荷甲神射手，一共在聯賽上陣33場轟入21球，貢獻12個助攻，他亦為首個在歐洲主流聯賽登上神射手寶座的亞洲球員。不過此子在今屆世盃表現乏善足陳，3場分組賽皆有上陣但未能取得入球，與隊友阿斯蒙都受到嚴厲指責。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180726/58486964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180726%2F58486964&d=jlsdZ6hoUHRkzPCMuPZ9aARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=85800abe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180726%2F58486964&h=cb4b2279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180726/58486964</a>"},{"pid":"064d9bfc37eee21aa2b189a06b897cb00666db4f","tid":756101,"uid":46042,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"係咪世界盃嗰個"},{"pid":"73385813335b590ee797e794fa1c00b4b7044ece","tid":756101,"uid":92376,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T18:00:36.000Z","msg":"李城又走寶<br />\n降班啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8849bb26665917a1aaf38f122b43ecc72e0ab95","tid":756101,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T18:01:07.000Z","msg":"諗咪最後唔入嗰球"},{"pid":"bdd5b7be86d87552f7cd19431205b1f8d27cd326","tid":756101,"uid":62073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid